snippet.title: Lone Ruin - Official Nintendo Switch and PC Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the trailer for roguelike twin-stick shooter, Lone Ruin. Optimize spells and build ultimate combos to defeat twisted monstrosities in this hellishly vibrant, highly addictive action game. Lone Ruin releases on Nintendo Switch and PC on January 12, 2023.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
